1
00:00:55,840 --> 00:00:56,800
Miss

2
00:00:56,880 --> 00:00:57,720
Spare me!

3
00:00:57,840 --> 00:00:58,760
Spare me!

4
00:00:59,240 --> 00:00:59,920
I admit it.

5
00:00:59,920 --> 00:01:02,920
I said the Cursed Day needed a sacrifice.

6
00:01:03,200 --> 00:01:06,200
I made all that up to scam money.

7
00:01:07,560 --> 00:01:10,200
But those people were killed by the Wang Family.

8
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:12,800
It really had nothing to do with me!

9
00:01:14,960 --> 00:01:17,200
Miss, wait, wait!

10
00:01:17,320 --> 00:01:18,600
If you can spare me,

11
00:01:19,440 --> 00:01:21,800
I'll give you all my money.

12
00:01:21,920 --> 00:01:23,080
All of it.

13
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:33,040
Shouldn't I have killed her?

14
00:01:34,320 --> 00:01:35,760
For her selfish desires,

15
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:38,040
she got so many innocent people killed.

16
00:01:38,240 --> 00:01:40,160
Including your daughter.

17
00:01:44,440 --> 00:01:45,880
Meigu has gone traveling.

18
00:01:45,960 --> 00:01:46,960
From today on,

19
00:01:47,080 --> 00:01:50,200
I'm Master Ai, head of Feng Shui Hall.

20
00:01:54,880 --> 00:01:56,560
Xu Nan and the Wang Family are innocent.

21
00:01:57,160 --> 00:01:58,240
Why would Yueya...

22
00:02:01,600 --> 00:02:03,880
Wang Yueya's target isn't just Wang Shengchang.

23
00:02:04,080 --> 00:02:05,360
It's everyone in the Wang Family.

24
00:02:05,560 --> 00:02:07,600
I'll help you save Xu Nan.

25
00:02:08,160 --> 00:02:10,520
For now, stay here.

26
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:12,200
Master, Master!

27
00:02:12,200 --> 00:02:13,360
You can't help her, Master!

28
00:02:15,280 --> 00:02:16,080
Master!

29
00:02:17,160 --> 00:02:19,480
Master, you can't help her, Master!

30
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:21,920
Master!

31
00:02:24,120 --> 00:02:28,760
That kid Zheng Yu won't ruin my plan, will he?

32
00:02:31,720 --> 00:02:33,800
Don't worry. He can't make it.

33
00:02:36,080 --> 00:02:38,880
There's something I still don't get.

34
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:41,320
This Sacrificial Ritual...

35
00:02:42,040 --> 00:02:44,360
Why hold it at the Wang Family estate?

36
00:02:46,200 --> 00:02:48,880
How many people have died on the Wang Family land?

37
00:02:49,200 --> 00:02:50,880
Yet it's still thriving.

38
00:02:51,040 --> 00:02:53,640
Doesn't that prove the Feng Shui here is excellent?

39
00:02:59,040 --> 00:03:00,480
Good, good.

40
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:04,120
I've arranged everything for today's ritual.

41
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:06,280
Then I'll leave it to Master Ai.

42
00:03:06,880 --> 00:03:07,840
Of course.

43
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:23,040
Fifth Concubine, Xiao Ru!

44
00:03:23,240 --> 00:03:24,440
I stole the key.

45
00:03:24,480 --> 00:03:26,080
They're preparing the ritual items.

46
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,320
This is the perfect chance to let you out.

47
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:29,880
Xiao Ru, I can't leave.

48
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:33,000
Fifth Concubine, if you don't go, you'll die!

49
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:34,680
Xiao Ru, listen to me.

50
00:03:35,320 --> 00:03:36,880
I'm going to avenge my sister.

51
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:38,320
I have to stay.

52
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,600
But don't worry.

53
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:42,680
I have a way to deal with Wang Shengchang.

54
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:44,560
If you really want to help me,

55
00:03:44,800 --> 00:03:45,960
go free Fatty.

56
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:47,840
He'll find Zheng Yu to save me.

57
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:50,840
Okay. I'll go right now.

58
00:03:50,920 --> 00:03:51,760
Be careful!

59
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:03,000
Master, you told me since I was little,

60
00:04:03,480 --> 00:04:05,360
every set of remains has its story.

61
00:04:06,040 --> 00:04:08,000
It records everything from their life.

62
00:04:08,760 --> 00:04:11,520
Death cannot bury the truth.

63
00:04:12,200 --> 00:04:14,320
I haven't forgotten I'm a Bone Collector.

64
00:04:14,320 --> 00:04:15,960
I know a Bone Collector's duty

65
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:18,960
is to protect all departed souls.

66
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:21,840
That's what you taught me.

67
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:24,480
Have you forgotten?

68
00:04:26,080 --> 00:04:27,400
The mistakes you've made

69
00:04:27,480 --> 00:04:29,040
can still be made right.

70
00:04:29,400 --> 00:04:30,720
Those departed souls

71
00:04:30,840 --> 00:04:32,040
need justice.

72
00:04:32,400 --> 00:04:34,320
They need us to give them justice, Master!

73
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:41,840
Zheng Yu!

74
00:04:42,200 --> 00:04:43,400
This is bad!

75
00:04:43,440 --> 00:04:45,080
The Wang Family caught Sister-in-law.

76
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:47,040
That maid secretly let me out.

77
00:04:47,200 --> 00:04:48,560
Let's hurry and rescue her.

78
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:50,520
Master told me everything.

79
00:04:50,840 --> 00:04:51,720
Who?

80
00:04:52,080 --> 00:04:53,080
Your Master.

81
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:54,880
Isn't he dead?

82
00:04:56,840 --> 00:04:59,360
He's not dead. He's been in Nanwan Town.

83
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:03,520
Yueya already drugged that Beast.

84
00:05:03,640 --> 00:05:07,760
Now that Beast only listens to her.

85
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:09,640
So that means...

86
00:05:10,080 --> 00:05:11,920
Master Ai is going on a killing spree.

87
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:13,360
Don't waste time.

88
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:13,920
Mix the medicine for me.

89
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:14,720
What are we mixing?

90
00:05:15,320 --> 00:05:16,240
Smoke Bombs.

91
00:05:16,640 --> 00:05:17,440
Okay.

92
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:21,520
One of each. Okay.

93
00:05:27,840 --> 00:05:28,800
Fifth Concubine.

94
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:30,200
Such a beautiful woman

95
00:05:30,320 --> 00:05:32,280
will fade like a flower tonight.

96
00:05:32,880 --> 00:05:35,440
Relax. The ritual will be over soon.

97
00:05:35,640 --> 00:05:37,720
I'll make your death quick.

98
00:05:37,960 --> 00:05:39,920
You're working with Wang Shengchang!

99
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:43,760
You helped the Wang Family do such evil.

100
00:05:43,840 --> 00:05:44,960
You'll die a horrible death!

101
00:05:45,120 --> 00:05:46,520
Save your strength.

102
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:47,920
Any last words?

103
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:49,000
Say them all at once.

104
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:50,920
I'll pass them to Brother Zheng Yu.

105
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:53,640
Zheng Yu saw your true colors long ago.

106
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:58,680
Master Ai.

107
00:06:00,880 --> 00:06:03,120
This Cursed Day sacrifice,

108
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:06,160
do we need to call everyone here?

109
00:06:06,320 --> 00:06:07,880
The more, the better.

110
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:10,240
That way we can gather yang energy

111
00:06:10,280 --> 00:06:11,640
to suppress evil spirits.

112
00:06:12,640 --> 00:06:13,520
Well...

113
00:06:13,760 --> 00:06:15,600
This ritual is no small matter.

114
00:06:15,760 --> 00:06:17,200
If he gets provoked,

115
00:06:17,280 --> 00:06:18,520
and he runs out,

116
00:06:18,760 --> 00:06:20,120
we'll be in big trouble.

117
00:06:22,200 --> 00:06:23,840
Master Ai is thorough.

118
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:26,400
Then let's begin.

119
00:06:28,280 --> 00:06:31,280
The Sacrificial Ritual needs kin's blood.

120
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:32,760
Master Wang.

121
00:06:34,640 --> 00:06:35,480
Forgive me for the offense.

122
00:07:04,080 --> 00:07:05,040
Come on.

123
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:11,240
Remember this taste well.

124
00:07:14,880 --> 00:07:15,720
What's wrong?

125
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:20,080
What's wrong?

126
00:07:21,200 --> 00:07:22,200
Master Ai.

127
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:24,000
Meigu said earlier,

128
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:28,080
after my son consumes forty-nine maidens,

129
00:07:28,240 --> 00:07:29,400
can the Sacrificial Ritual be held.

130
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:32,400
We're still missing one.

131
00:07:33,280 --> 00:07:34,720
Time waits for no one.

132
00:07:34,960 --> 00:07:35,880
No matter.

133
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:38,040
I'm already prepared.

134
00:07:40,080 --> 00:07:40,960
Bring her in.

135
00:07:44,520 --> 00:07:45,320
Xiao Ru!

136
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:48,640
Master, what are you doing?

137
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:52,200
You think I don't know what you've done?

138
00:07:52,440 --> 00:07:54,320
Wang Shengchang, let her go!

139
00:07:54,320 --> 00:07:55,720
This has nothing to do with her.

140
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:57,480
In our Wang Family,

141
00:07:58,000 --> 00:08:01,800
any act of defiance leads to one road,

142
00:08:02,440 --> 00:08:04,040
and that is death.

143
00:08:04,840 --> 00:08:06,880
Fifth Concubine, no need to say more.

144
00:08:07,640 --> 00:08:08,440
After all,

145
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:10,560
a Beast can't understand human words.

146
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:14,920
Xiao Ru!

147
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:16,400
Let me go!

148
00:08:16,440 --> 00:08:17,760
You bunch of Beasts!

149
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:19,120
Spare her, or you'll die a horrible death!

150
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:20,400
Aren't you after me?

151
00:08:23,400 --> 00:08:24,320
Xiao Ru!

152
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:28,080
Wang Shengchang!

153
00:08:28,280 --> 00:08:29,560
You've lost all conscience!

154
00:08:29,560 --> 00:08:30,800
You're inhuman!

155
00:08:30,880 --> 00:08:32,720
Aren't you afraid of heaven's retribution?

156
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:34,880
In Nanwan Town,

157
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:37,640
I am heaven!

158
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:39,680
I am heaven!

159
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:42,600
Master Wang, begin.

160
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:48,920
Tonight,

161
00:08:49,720 --> 00:08:51,640
none of you are getting away.
